LogicalTable.name: D0 Time
LogicalTable.Description: This logical table maps to the physical Time Dimension tables at Day and Month grains. It federatess 2 distinct physical tables : one at the Day grain level, one at the month level. BIEE server will pick the most appropriate source based on the context of each user query.

LogicalColumn.name: Calendar Date
LogicalColumn.Description: Calendar Date uniquely identifies each record in the Time dimension table. Stores the date information in the format MM/DD/YYYY. Eg :- 11/12/2006

AttributeDefn.name: AttributeDefn
AttributeDefn.ExprTextDesc: "Sample App Lite Data"."".""."D01 Time Day Grain"."Calendar_Date"

LogicalColumn.name: Per Name Week
LogicalColumn.Description: Per Name Week- Stores the week information in the format YYYY Week Number. Eg :- 2005 Week 44

AttributeDefn.name: AttributeDefn
AttributeDefn.ExprTextDesc: "Sample App Lite Data"."".""."D01 Time Day Grain"."Per_Name_Week"

LogicalColumn.name: Per Name Month
LogicalColumn.Description: Per Name Month. Stores the month information in the format YYYY / MM. Eg :- 2006 / 11

AttributeDefn.name: AttributeDefn
AttributeDefn.ExprTextDesc: "Sample App Lite Data"."".""."D01 Time Day Grain"."Per_Name_Month"

LogicalColumn.name: Per Name Qtr

AttributeDefn.ExprTextDesc: "Sample App Lite Data"."".""."D01 Time Day Grain"."Per_Name_Qtr"

AttributeDefn.name: AttributeDefn
AttributeDefn.ExprTextDesc: "Sample App Lite Data"."".""."D01 Time Day Grain"."Per_Name_Half"
